text: Ekalal Shrestha ((Nepali: एकलाल श्रेष्ठ) is Nepalese politician, belonging to Communist Party of Nepal (Unified Marxist–Leninist). He is currently serving as Minister for Labour, Employment and Transport of Bagmati Province and also member of the Bagmati Provincial Assembly. == References == Category:Communist Party of Nepal (Unified Marxist–Leninist) politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Ekalal Shrestha
